# System Design

- **Event-driven:** Services communicate via Redis pub/sub, not direct HTTP for pipeline flow.
- **Async-first:** Use async I/O for all external calls (DB, Redis, HTTP).
- **Provider abstraction:** Each capability (LLM, image, TTS) has LOCAL/CLOUD strategy.
- **CQRS-lite:** Separate read models for analytics; write through domain events.
